<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q15_v14" title="Q15_v14" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceD</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En la ficha de un evento solidario se registró lo siguiente:</p>
    <p>
      - Asistentes al evento: <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math><br />
      - Asistentes que no donaron dinero: <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math><br />
      - Entre quienes donaron, el <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> se comprometió con una donación mensual.
    </p>
    <p>Según estos datos, ¿qué porcentaje de todos los asistentes se comprometió con una donación mensual?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">0,9%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si se considera un total de <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math> asistentes, <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> no donó, así que sí donó <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>. De ese grupo, el <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> se comprometió mensualmente, entonces <m:math><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> del total. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>0,9</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">5,1%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Tomando <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math> asistentes, los que donaron son <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn></m:math>. Luego, quienes se comprometieron con donación mensual son <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>85</m:mn></m:math>, es decir <m:math><m:mn>0,60</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn></m:math>. Eso corresponde a <m:math><m:mn>51</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> del total, no a <m:math><m:mn>5,1</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">9%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. De todos los asistentes, primero hay que calcular cuántos donaron: <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>. Después, el porcentaje que se comprometió mensualmente es <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de ese <m:math><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>0,60</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso, el porcentaje buscado es <m:math><m:mn>51</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> y no <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">51%<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si el total de asistentes es <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> no donó, entonces donó <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>. Entre ellos, el <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> se comprometió con una donación mensual, por lo que el porcentaje de todos los asistentes es <m:math><m:mn>0,60</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>51</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar el total</strong></p>
            <p>El total de asistentes representa <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el porcentaje que sí donó</strong></p>
            <p>Como el <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> no donó, el porcentaje que sí donó es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular quiénes se comprometieron con donación mensual</strong></p>
            <p>Entre quienes donaron, el <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> se comprometió mensualmente. Entonces se calcula el <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>0,60</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, el porcentaje buscado es <m:math><m:mn>51</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con una interpretación sobre 100 asistentes</strong></p>
            <p>Si hubiera <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math> asistentes, <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:math> no donarían y <m:math><m:mn>85</m:mn></m:math> sí donarían.</p>
            <p>De esos <m:math><m:mn>85</m:mn></m:math>, el <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>0,60</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>85</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Así, <m:math><m:mn>51</m:mn></m:math> de cada <m:math><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:math> asistentes se comprometieron con una donación mensual.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La respuesta correcta es <strong>51%</strong>, correspondiente a la alternativa D.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>